OL,6,FThe former MP for Blackpool South will
OL,7,Fbe suspended after his appeal against
OL,8,Fthe Standards Committee's decision was
OL,9,Fdismissed by an independent panel.
OL,11,FScott Benton will be given the 35 day
OL,12,Frecommended suspension after an
OL,13,Findependent panel dismissed his appeal.
OL,15,FFollowing his suspension decision, a
OL,16,Frecall petition will be triggered in
OL,17,Fhis constituency for a .
