OL,6,FThe Commons standard watchdog
OL,7,Frecommended a 35 day suspension but
OL,8,FBenton appealed the decision, saying
OL,9,Fhis actions were an "extremely serious
OL,10,Fbreach."
OL,12,FHe claimed it was "was heavily
OL,13,Finfluenced by the memorandum submitted
OL,14,Fby the Parliamentary Commissioner for
OL,15,FStandards which makes several pivotal
OL,16,Fstatements that are completely
OL,17,Ffactually inaccurate".
