OL,6,FHe added: "If those that judge MPs are
OL,7,Fnot being open minded, fair and
OL,8,Fproportionate in the way that they are
OL,9,Fhandling evidence or examining
OL,10,Fwitnesses, our democracy is under
OL,11,Fthreat."
OL,13,FHe said he believed a second
OL,14,Fassessment will "consider the facts
OL,15,Fand lead to a more equitable decision".
