OL,6,FThe independent panel dismissed both
OL,7,Farguments, saying there was "no
OL,8,Fsubstance" to his claims against the
OL,9,Fcommissioner and that an investigation
OL,10,Fby the Standards Committee found there
OL,11,Fhad been no leak of its decision.
OL,13,FThe panel also found there was "no
OL,14,Fsubstance" to Mr Benton's claims that
OL,15,Fthe recommended suspension was
OL,16,F"unreasonable and/or disproportionate".
