OL,6,FThe Government will now move the
OL,7,Fproposal to suspend Mr Benton, which
OL,8,Fis likely to pass the Commons without
OL,9,Fdifficulty, triggering the six-week
OL,10,Flong recall petition process.
OL,12,FIf 10% of Mr Benton's constituents
OL,13,Fsign the petition, he will be recalled
OL,14,Fand a by-election will take place,
OL,15,Fmeaning the poll is unlikely to occur
OL,16,Funtil the end of April or the
OL,17,Fbeginning of May.
