OL,6,FJonathan Ashworth, the shadow
OL,7,Fpaymaster general, said: "Scott Benton
OL,8,Fshould do the decent thing and resign,
OL,9,Fsaving the people of Blackpool South a
OL,10,Flengthy recall petition that would
OL,11,Fleave them without the representation
OL,12,Fthey deserve.
OL,14,F"This is yet another by-election
OL,15,Fcaused by Tory scandal. Britain
OL,16,Fdeserves better than this carousel of
OL,17,FConservative chaos.
OL,19,F"Labour's Chris Webb is Blackpool born
OL,20,Fand bred, and ready to deliver a fresh
OL,21,Fstart for Blackpool South."
