OL,6,FIn response, Mr Benton has said he is
OL,7,F"deeply disappointed" by the decision
OL,8,Fand described the findings as
OL,9,F"unjust", with an "inescapable
OL,10,Fappearance of bias".
OL,12,FHe went on to say the contents of the
OL,13,Freport "were leaked to the press" and
OL,14,Fthe report ignored "clear and
OL,15,Funequivocal evidence of such leaks".
