OL,6,FHe added: "It goes without saying that
OL,7,Fthe Standards process is designed to
OL,8,Fbe open, fair, honest and transparent
OL,9,Fso the public and MPs can have trust
OL,10,Fin it. These events clearly mean that
OL,11,Fthis trust has been breached by
OL,12,FMembers of the Committee and/or its
OL,13,Fadministrative staff and create an
OL,14,Finevitable perception of partiality.
